Cell["\<\
Do the Monte Carlo simulation. Without specifying the measurement, all bare \
fermion modes are monitored:\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->1494923699,ExpressionUUID->"fc624313-08ad-41d2-a3bc-b5c9ebee54e5"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[{
 RowBox[{
